{"tid":1628103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"4個月啦 你地仲味學識...","createTime":"2019-10-06T00:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:42:42.000Z","uid":110878,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"171abc948f031820e7928d0bd78920f4471d6f6b","tid":1628103,"uid":110878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"就係上連登勿認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋總有堆人鐘意極端咁沒黑一堆人，<br />\n勇武又好，和理非又好，網上鳩噏從來唔洗負責，<br />\n我係政府都派d打手黎鳩噏分化你地，睇你地互鬧幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奉勸各位自己思考，你為咩而企出黎。我相各位都係有智商既人，唔好因為網上留言動搖你自己。<br />\n裝修既討論都夠多，前線都唔係傻。<br />\n和理非既負出都唔係白費。<br />\n都係果句啦，香港人無本錢再輸啦。<br />\n和勇一體繼續走洛去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60f02f8dc952f17469ac5d15ae4497f775de958","tid":1628103,"uid":33463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:06:16.000Z","msg":"團結力量大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d21d3a8ff3180601e0b8280aeefdfb401ffbc0","tid":1628103,"uid":110878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:07:33.000Z","msg":"總有理由令你繼續走洛去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adb6b75f4d72357fb1cea85fdfbc03a5b642880","tid":1628103,"uid":110878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9347374234de2926dc6f232e25f0fe69b3087a5","tid":1628103,"uid":179679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score"